FBIS4-63194 "drsov098_b_94034" FBIS-SOV-94-098 Daily Report 17 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Issues Tu-160 Bomber Production Halted Tu-160 Bomber Production Halted PM2005081594 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1325 GMT 17 May 94 PM2005081594 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "M-Trust" program: Announcer-read report over video of Tu-160] [Text] The Kazan Aviation Association named for Gorbunov has halted production of the Tu-160 strategic missile carriers, the POSTFAKTUM AERO Agency reports. Each such plane costs several billion rubles. The last few to have been produced are yet to be claimed and paid for by the Army. They remain at the plant.
